utiers - Hl. Joachim lesend GG 375x.jpg|center|128px]]\n|''[[Saint Joachim Reading a Book]]''\n| [[Kunsthistorisches Museum]]\n| GG_375\n| 1650\n| <ref>RKD # 37759</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina Woutiers - St. Joseph GG 376x.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[Saint Joseph (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''Saint Joseph'']]\n| [[Kunsthistorisches Museum]]\n| GG_376\n| 1650\n| <ref>RKD # 37757</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Wautier-doper.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[John the Baptist (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''John the Baptist'']]\n| [[Museo L\u00e1zaro Galdiano]]\n| 84\n| 1650\n| \n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina Woutiers - St. Joachim GG 1911.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[Saint Joachim (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''Saint Joachim'']]\n| [[Kunsthistorisches Museum]]\n| GG_1911\n| 1650\n| <ref>RKD # 37758</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Wautier-holofernes.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[Judith with the Head of Holofernes and her Maid (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''Judith with the Head of Holofernes and her Maid'']]\n| [[Sint-Waldetrudiskerk]]\n| \n| 1650 \n| <ref>BALaT # 32252</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Elk zijn meug.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[['To Each his Own' (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''To Each his Own'']]\n| [[The Phoebus Foundation]]\n| \n| 1650\n| <ref>[https://www.van-ham.com/datenbank-archiv/datenbank/michaelina-wautier/elk-zijn-meug-jeder-nach-seinem-geschmack.html Auction record]</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Wautier-Gehoor.jpg|center|128px]]\n| ''Hearing''\n| private collection\n| \n| 1650 \n| <ref name=RH>[https://www.digitalekunstkrant.nl/rubenshuis-zoekt-vermiste-schilderijen-michaelina-wautier/ Rubenshuis]</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina-Wautier-Retrato-Smeets.jpg|center|128px]]\n|''[[Portrait of an Officer, possibly Pierre Wautier]]''\n| private collection\n| \n| 1650\n| \n|-\n| [[File:Wautier-tobacco.jpg|center|128px]]\n| ''Tobacco'' (Smell?)\n| private collection\n| \n| 1650\n| \n|-\n| [[File:Wautier-studie jonge vrouw.jpg|center|128px]]\n| ''Study of a Young Woman''\n| private collection\n| \n| 1650\n| \n|-\n| [[File:Wautier-evangelist.jpg|center|128px]]\n|''[[Portrait histori\u00e9 of a Young Man as John the Evangelist]]''\n| private collection\n| \n| 1650\n| \n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina Woutiers, Blumengirlande mit Prachtlibelle, 1652.jpg|center|128px]]\n|''[[Flower Garland with Dragonfly]]''\n| private collection\n| \n| 1652\n| \n|-\n| [[File:Guirlande-Wautier.jpg|center|128px]]\n|''[[Flower Garland with Butterfly]]''\n| private collection\n| \n| 1652\n| <ref name=RH/>\n|-\n| [[File:Portrait of Martino Martini by Michaelina Wautier.jpg|center|128px]]\n|''[[Portrait of Martino Martini]] (1614\u20131661), Jesuit missionary in China''\n| private collection\n| \n| 1654\n| <ref>RKD # 277987</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina wautier-retrato de joven.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[Portrait of a Young Man (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''Portrait of a Young Man'']]\n| [[Royal Museum of Fine Arts Antwerp]]\n| 5149\n| 1655\n| <ref>RKD # 286231</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina wautier-educaci\u00f3n de la virgen.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[The Education of the Virgin (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''The Education of the Virgin'']], with possible self-portrait\n| private collection\n| \n| 1656\n| <ref>RKD # 236335</ref> <ref>BALaT # 40001189</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina wautier-joven fumando en pipa.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[Young Man Smoking a Pipe (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''Young Man Smoking a Pipe'']]\n| private collection\n| \n| 1656\n| \n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina wautier-anunciaci\u00f3n.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[The Annunciation (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''The Annunciation'']]\n| [[mus\u00e9e-promenade de Marly-le-Roi]]\n| 77.30.1\n| 1659\n| <ref>BALaT # 40001196</ref>\n|}\n\n==Sources==\n* [https://www.mas.be/en/michaelina Exhibition website] by [[Museum aan de Stroom]]\n*''Michaelina Wautier (1614\u20131689)'', catalog and 2018 art exhibition in Antwerp, by Katlijne Van der Stighelen, 2018. [https://www.mas.be/sites/mas/files/MAS_Michaelina_gids_EN.pdf Handbook for exhibition]\n* [https://rkd.nl/explore/artists/85684 RKD record] for Michaelina Wautier\n* BALat record for Michaelina Wautier in [[Royal Institute for Cultural Heritage]]\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n{{Michaelina Wautier|state=expanded}}\n{{Lists of paintings}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of paintings|Wautier]]\n[[Category:Paintings by Michaelina Wautier| ]]\n", "text_old": "The following is a '''list of paintings by [[Michaelina Wautier]]''' that are generally accepted as autograph by the [[Katlijne Van der Stighelen]] catalog and other sources. \n\n{| class='wikitable sortable' style='width:100%'\n!image\n!title\n!collection\n!inventory number\n!year\n!reference\n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina Wautier - self-portrait with easel.jpg|center|128px]]\n|''[[Self-portrait with Easel]]''\n| private collection\n| \n| 1640s\n| <ref>RKD #236337</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Jacob van Oost (I) - Two boys blowing bubbles.jpg|center|128px]]\n|''[[Two Boys Blowing Bubbles]]''\n| [[Seattle Art Museum]]\n| 58.140\n| 1640s\n| <ref>[https://slog.thestranger.com/2008/07/whose_bubbles_1 blog about attribution]</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Wautier-commandant spaans leger.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[Portrait of a Commander in the Spanish Army|''Portrait of an Officer'']]\n| [[Royal Museums of Fine Arts of Belgium]]\n| 297\n| 1646\n| <ref>BALaT # 20025819</ref>\n|- \n| [[File:Michaelina wautier-desposorios m\u00edsticos.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[The Mystical Marriage of Saint Catherine of Alexandria (Painting by Michaelina Wautier)|''The Mystical Marriage of Saint Catherine of Alexandria'']]\n| Diocesan Seminary,  [[Namur]]\n| \n| 1649\n| <ref>BALaT # 10129426</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:Michaelina woutiers-santas ines y dorotea.jpg|center|128px]]\n|[[Two Girls as Saint Agnes and Saint Dorothea |''Saint Agnes and Saint Dorothea'']]\n| [[Royal Museum of Fine Arts Antwerp]]\n| 599\n| 1650s\n| <ref>RKD # 61786</ref> <ref>[http://vlaamsekunstcollectie.be/collection/work/data/599 599]{{Dead link|date=March 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted