o.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?serviceGbn=ALL&termGbn=week&hitYear=2015&targetTime=35&nationGbn=E|title=Gaon Digital Chart \u2013 Week 32, 2015|publisher=[[Gaon Music Chart|Gaon]]|language=Korean|accessdate=August 27, 2015}}</ref>\n| 12\n|-\n{{singlechart|Switzerland|21|artist=Fifth Harmony|song=Worth It|accessdate=5 July 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|UK|3|date=2015-07-16|accessdate=July 10, 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardhot100|12|artist=Fifth Harmony|accessdate=24 June 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardadultpopsongs|22|artist=Fifth Harmony|accessdate=4 August 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboarddanceairplay|5|artist=Fifth Harmony|accessdate=4 August 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardlatinairplay|48|artist=Fifth Harmony|accessdate=22 November 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardpopsongs|4|artist=Fifth Harmony|accessdate=4 August 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardrhythmic|19|artist=Fifth Harmony|accessdate=28 July 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardlatintropical|25|artist=Fifth Harmony|accessdate=22 November 2015|rowheader=true}}\n|}\n<!-- Before adding any other US charts please review/consult [[WP:BILLBOARDCHARTS#Single charts]] & [[WP:CHARTMATH]]. -->\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Year-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"| Chart (2015)\n!scope=\"col\"| Position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aria.com.au/aria-charts-end-of-year-charts-top-100-singles-2015.htm|title=ARIA Charts - End of Year Charts - Top 100 Singles 2015|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|accessdate=January 6, 2016}}</ref>\n| 62\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Belgium (Ultratop 50 Flanders)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=2015&cat=s|title=Jaaroverzichten 2015\t|publisher=[[Ultratop]]|accessdate=March 29, 2016}}</ref>\n| 55\n|-\n! scope=\"